{{Otheruses|Sullustan}}
'''Sullustan gin''' was an [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage that was produced on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]]. Having a light flavor, it was used as a base for other recipes.<ref name="swg">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=item|Sullustan Gin}}</ref> It was one of the ingredients for [[Sonic Servodriver]] and [[Ice blaster]]s. It was also a favorite beverage of [[Lady/Legends|Lady]] [[Valarian/Legends|Valarian]] and was used in the making of [[Wookiee-wango]]s.

